uement made about how bad the US government is/has been in the past, 10 arguements can be made for the US and its great history on such issues. Contrast that with just about any other county in history and there is some perspective to be gained.<img src="images/bigeyes_125.gif" border="0" alt="" title="" align="middle" /><br /><br /></span id="msg"></font><br><br></td>
